These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, mirinda, tea
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, indonesian, dutch, russian
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, frog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, fantasy, martial-arts
 1. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
 2. the person drinking milk is the russian##1
 3. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the dutch is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the right of the dutch##1
 9. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Beverage    | mirinda   | milk       | almond-milk | tea   |
| Nationality        | indonesian    | russian  | dutch      | japanese |
| Pet         | frog      | chinchilla | dog         | cat   |
| Movie-Genre   | action | crime       | fantasy        | martial-arts   |

