.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, peach, potato
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, gospel, indie, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski, bike, taxi
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, 7up, tea
 1. the fan of indie is the person eating peach##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person driving the tram is between the person drinking 7up and the fan of gospel##2
 9. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
10. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Food          | grapefruit | potato  | cauliflower | peach      |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | rock    | gospel      | indie      |
| Transport           | taxi     | tram     | jet-ski         | bike   |
| Beverage         | 7up | iced-tea | coffee     | tea |

