3. the person driving the van is the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's birthday is in march##2
9. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Transport           | quad-bike     | helicopter | train | van |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family       | epic      | scientific   |
| Birthday   | december   | november   | march    | august       |
