There 4 different types of food: carrot, kiwi, pineapple, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, metal, reggae, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, spanish, indonesian
 1. the british is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the indonesian##1
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 8. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the egyptian##1
10. the fan of trance is between the person traveling to nizza and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| City      | edinburgh | nizza | boston     | colone       |
| Food          | carrot   | zucchini    | pineapple | kiwi       |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | metal       | trance    | reggae     |
| Nationality         | spanish  | indonesian  | british | egyptian |

