The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, ice-hockey, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the wooden house##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the wooden house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking fanta##1
10. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
11. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |     4     |
