There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red, chestnut, green
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, horror, spy, superhero
1. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes green is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching spy movies is between the person who likes yellow and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
6. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
8. the person who likes yellow is between the person watching comedy movies and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |      4       |
| Game          | backgammon | bridge | mah-jongg      | chess    |
| Hobby         | traveling   | dancing  | board-games | magic-tricks |
