.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, radish, watermelon
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, coffee, mirinda
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, trance, disco, dubstep
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the fan of disco and the fan of trance##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person drinking lemonade and the fan of rock##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person eating radish is the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | blueberry | watermelon   | radish   | artichoke |
| Beverage           | juice   | coffee     | lemonade   | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Music-Genre         | rock    | trance | dubstep | disco    |

 